# Conventional Commit message template
#
# Format:
#   type(scope): subject
#
# Examples:
#   feat(ui): add drag-and-drop upload
#   fix(llm): handle empty chunks
#   refactor(llm,ui,test): align separator cleanup and ui defaults
#
# Allowed types: feat fix docs style refactor perf test build ci chore revert
# Scope: optional, lowercase, supports commas for multiple scopes

